author: Pitchfork
title: Lana Del Rey Teases Mysterious Date Sequence
text:
Lana Del Rey Teases Mysterious Date Sequence “Ingredients can be found online” Lana Del Rey Photo by FOX via Getty Images 
Lana Del Rey recently made her return with a new song, “ Love .” Now, the singer-songwriter has teased a series of dates on her Twitter, accompanied with a cryptic message. “At the stroke of midnight... Feb 24, March 26, April 24, May 23,” it reads. “Ingredients can b found online.” Check out the tweet below; it’s unclear if Del Rey is hinting at the release dates for more new music, or something entirely different. The dates also happen to line up with the “ waning crescent moon ritual dates ” observed by members of the occult. Del Rey’s last studio album, Honeymoon , arrived in 2015. At the stroke of midnight Feb 24, March 26, April 24, May 23❤️
